com.stabilit.sc.srv.cmd
Interface IPassThrough

public interface IPassThrough

The Interface IPassThrough. Marks commands which pass through messages. Is used to decide if a part message arrives, has to be queued and await completion before pass it over to the command or pass it over directly.
